thread.title: SHARON
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by SHARON

author: SHARON
title: SHARON
text: Lovely friendly service at airport counter - a bonus to be able to sort everything from the terminal. Very happy with size, presentation and cost of the vehicle. Vehicle itself certainly not a high performance vehicle that I would be in a hurry to own, but served the purpose we needed it for more than adequately.
